=== Description ===
JobYourself is a non-profit based in Brussels that provides the opportunity to those who want to create their own job to develop an enterprise project and to test in a structured and safe environment. It operates within three activity cooperatives: Baticrea, Bruxelles-Emergences and debut. The hope to support entrepreneurship and strengthen the members of the cooperative activities by sharing expertise and experience through the framework of a unique team.

Bruxelles-Emergences is a cooperative activity that accompanies all business sectors (except construction).

